<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٥٩:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {كَذَّبَتْ ثَمُودُ وَعَادٌ بِالْقَارِعَةِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> فَأَمَّا ثَمُودُ فَأُهْلِكُوا بِالطَّاغِيَةِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>} <span class="c4">[الحاقة: ٤، ٥]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c3">{بِالطَّاغِيَةِ}</span>: بِطُغْيَانِهِمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>